{"tid":712406,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖球迷 打死阿根廷球員","createTime":"2018-06-22T05:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T05:47:58.000Z","uid":48834,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"caad21e36e1fa03e51ffa4ef586963e2b32ed521","tid":712406,"uid":48834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:18:57.000Z","msg":"阿根廷球員尼圖（FrancoNieto）日前喺一場比賽之後畀球迷打死！事件發生喺上星期六一場阿根廷丙組聯賽迪羅聯邦對查卡里塔青年，由於雙方球員喺比賽最後15分鐘時上演群毆，執法球證總共出示咗八張紅牌，而比賽亦因此停咗15分鐘。據報道，其中迪羅聯邦隊長尼圖同太太以及一個月大嘅囡囡準備上車離開嘅時候，畀三個人圍住拳打腳踢，其中一個人仲用磚頭襲擊佢個頭而令佢昏迷，尼圖喺星期二接受咗手術可惜不幸喺星期三死亡。當地警方表示已經拘捕咗三個男人，希望所有球迷都可以理智，唔好再有慘劇發生啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20141205/53198439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20141205%2F53198439&d=FvZG0cN0CA52FazMClOsuKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=dbddbf86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20141205%2F53198439&h=37ee4c59\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20141205/53198439</a>"},{"pid":"0823086f0193e50f515e40931cb1fbc0e9e72ae8","tid":712406,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"又係賭輸波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打人果個好慘 又輸錢又要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd63007c7bea87b3ea5931e6d33e797d208981d9","tid":712406,"uid":67252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"下個到邊個"},{"pid":"c41254cbec90235e441237515f4676a144502f8c","tid":712406,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"小花住係西班牙既"}]}